Developed an end-to-end Data Engineering pipeline using PySpark, dbt, Apache Airflow, Docker, and DuckDB. Implemented Medallion Architecture (Bronze, Silver, Gold) to ingest, transform, and aggregate e-commerce datasets. Automated data workflows using Airflow DAGs, created reusable data models with dbt, and generated lineage documentation. Integrated local cloud services using Floci and version-controlled the project with GitHub.
